		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Founded in 2020, AquaLuxe was born from a vision to merge sustainable practices with luxury design in the world of aquatic fixtures. We believe that water is a precious resource, and our relationship with it should be both beautiful and responsible.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>To innovate and lead the market in eco-friendly luxury water systems, providing our customers with unparalleled design, quality, and service while championing water conservation efforts globally.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
